# Review & Continuous Improvement of Cybersecurity Risk Management Strategy – Audit Checklist

## 1. Defined Review Process
- [ ] Does the organization have a defined process for reviewing the outcomes of its cybersecurity risk management strategy?

**Audit Evidence / Prüfpunkte:**
- Dokumentierter Review-Zyklus für Cybersecurity-Strategie
- Genehmigung durch Management / CISO
- Integration in Governance- oder ISMS-Prozesse
- Historie der Review-Meetings

---

## 2. Data & Metrics Collection
- [ ] How does the organization identify and collect relevant data and metrics to evaluate the effectiveness of its cybersecurity risk management strategy?

**Audit Evidence / Prüfpunkte:**
- KPI/KRI für Cybersecurity-Strategie
- Datenquellen dokumentiert (Logs, Reports, Dashboards)
- Nachweis der Datenerhebung und -verarbeitung
- Tools und Methoden zur Analyse der Wirksamkeit

---

## 3. Roles & Responsibilities
- [ ] Are there clear roles and responsibilities assigned for the review and analysis of cybersecurity risk management strategy outcomes?

**Audit Evidence / Prüfpunkte:**
- RACI-Matrix oder Governance-Dokumentation
- Benannte Personen / Teams für Analyse und Reporting
- Verantwortlichkeiten in Policies verankert
- Nachweis von Schulungen und Awareness

---

## 4. Stakeholder Feedback Mechanisms
- [ ] What mechanisms are in place to gather feedback and input from key stakeholders (leadership, business units, cybersecurity team) on the strategy's effectiveness?

**Audit Evidence / Prüfpunkte:**
- Stakeholder-Meetings oder Workshops
- Surveys oder Feedback-Formulare
- Dokumentation der Ergebnisse
- Integration des Feedbacks in Strategie-Reviews

---

## 5. Consideration of Environmental Changes
- [ ] Does the review process consider changes in the threat landscape, regulatory environment, technology, and business objectives that may impact the strategy?

**Audit Evidence / Prüfpunkte:**
- Threat Intelligence und Regulierungsupdates dokumentiert
- Technologie- und Business-Impact-Analysen
- Anpassungen in Review-Protokollen
- Managemententscheidungen basierend auf Änderungen

---

## 6. Analysis & Identification of Improvements
- [ ] How does the organization analyse the results of the review to identify areas for improvement or adjustment?

**Audit Evidence / Prüfpunkte:**
- Nachweis von Gap-Analysen oder Lessons Learned
- Dokumentierte Verbesserungsvorschläge
- Priorisierung von Anpassungsmaßnahmen
- Reports an Management / Steering Committee

---

## 7. Incorporation into Decision-Making
- [ ] Are there documented procedures for incorporating the findings from the review into decision-making and strategic planning?

**Audit Evidence / Prüfpunkte:**
- Dokumentierte Prozesse zur Integration der Review-Ergebnisse
- Protokolle von Strategie- oder Managementmeetings
- Nachweis der Umsetzung von Anpassungen
- Verknüpfung zu Budget- und Ressourcenentscheidungen

---

## 8. Leadership Commitment
- [ ] How does leadership demonstrate their commitment to the continuous improvement of the cybersecurity risk management strategy based on the review outcomes?

**Audit Evidence / Prüfpunkte:**
- Teilnahme von Führungskräften an Review-Meetings
- Ressourcenbereitstellung für Verbesserungsmaßnahmen
- Kommunikation des Engagements an Mitarbeitende
- Integration von Review-Ergebnissen in strategische Entscheidungen

---

## 9. Monitoring Implementation & Impact
- [ ] Does the organization have a process to monitor the implementation and impact of any adjustments made to the strategy based on the review findings?

**Audit Evidence / Prüfpunkte:**
- Nachweis der Umsetzung von Anpassungen
- KPI/KRI Monitoring zur Wirksamkeit
- Follow-up Audits oder Reviews
- Management-Reporting über Verbesserungsmaßnahmen
